\id JUD - Tabo (Aramia dialect) NT - Papua New Guinea 2006 (DBL 2014) 
\h Yud 
\toc3 Yud 
\toc1 Yudakono Leta Yudakono Leta 
\toc2 Yuda 
\mt1 YUDAKONO LETA  
\mt2 EBETE HIBIMAęž‰ MIDIPAęž‰TAMO ODODIYAęž‰  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Na baęž‰ Yudate, Yaęž‰su Kelisokono okodawa etala baęž‰gala Yaęž‰imesikono ekawila.  
\p Laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi Nabiwi Godote dopamo daęž‰kaęž‰lamiyaęž‰la, iyo, ebete laęž‰ pui malemalelo demalagidolena baęž‰gala Yaęž‰su Kelisokono itaguaęž‰midale ipuwalo demedehonama, na baęž‰moe leta laęž‰tamo poememo.   
\p
\v 2 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala hete komo baęž‰gala lumagitamo kuba huiya ikamehaęž‰ komo baęž‰gala malemale emalagidolo komo, baęž‰moi netewa-kapiya komate laęž‰godolo konomamo naęž‰polaęž‰namenaęž‰.   
\s1 Godote Kuba Ododilipaęž‰tamo Huiya Ikalame Komo  
\p
\v 3-4 Naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, ale Godogodone kapimilo daęž‰lawiyaęž‰maęž‰, na dopamo baęž‰be kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komomaęž‰ leta ipuwalo olamagimaęž‰ ewagelimo. Huiyatiya baęž‰ma tetelo eta ukuiti natamo aęž‰pi, mabu nale baęž‰moe komo ulimo, Godokono ubi komamo papamilaęž‰hahaęž‰ dubate laęž‰eno kapiyuimi ipuwamo diya gabodo aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰laęž‰huyaęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ na ubila baęž‰moe eta komamo laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na kowalubilimaęž‰, Godote a ebeno tawakalubaęž‰tamo dikaaęž‰miyaęž‰, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰be hibimaęž‰ midi komomaęž‰ helonomamo nalaholonakuyaęž‰laęž‰.  
\p Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰bakobako dubate Godokono malemale hawakalimino tabo hiyaęž‰maęž‰ miditi naęž‰gaęž‰lanaka, lumagiti kuba dododimini Godote huiya aęž‰kikamaęž‰mene mabu ebeno malemale konomola, baęž‰gala ibaęž‰te naęž‰kagaęž‰lana Yaęž‰su Kelisoko hibi kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰dawahaęž‰. Aęž‰iye, ebe kapiya baęž‰ aeno hibi Namutudawala baęž‰gala Kodawala, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ibino kuba mabumaęž‰ Godokono Buka tabote yaęž‰lo tetenomolo aęž‰goiyaęž‰, galane ibaęž‰te ibino temeteme huiya hibilo kolawemaęž‰naęž‰!  
\v 5 Iyo, Godote kuba ododilipaęž‰tamo huiya dikalamemene, laęž‰ baęž‰be komo dopamo iyaęž‰tawahuyaęž‰mata, huiyatiya na ubila kebe olalati komote Godokono Isalaela tawakalubaęž‰tamo duluhukuyaęž‰, laęž‰ baęž‰moe komo gala naęž‰kemalagidolalaęž‰. Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godote ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰lelamelo Isipiti hopone ibi duluhukulateliyaęž‰, gala hapuni komo ibaęž‰te ebe hibimaęž‰ kamidiyaęž‰haęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebete ibi dito anakapulamiyaęž‰.  
\v 6 Baęž‰gala baęž‰moe eta komo naęž‰kumaęž‰laęž‰, tupuimi mabuni Hunu Haboeno komo nopopaęž‰te ibino hido emede haba miyaęž‰pate Godotamo alaholo komo baęž‰bo tupuimiyaęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ Godote ibi taęž‰tehohaęž‰ auli halaęž‰mo matuhulameholete du ipuwamo dito iyaęž‰hekiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te baęž‰bolo ibino kuba huiya uwatemaęž‰ Godokono Ko Hegela kolatiminamaęž‰.  
\v 7 Baęž‰gala wadiyala laęž‰ Sodomo habanapi baęž‰gala Gomola habanapi baęž‰gala ibi tamelo demedehonamaęž‰ baęž‰bi habahabanapi ibino komo atumu naęž‰kemalagidolalaęž‰. Ibi hiliyonomate atumu Godokono kukala badikamidaliyaęž‰, baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ibi ipuwalo etate etatamo kateneno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kuba ubi komokomo bododilinakuyaęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ Godote ibino kuba huiya ibaęž‰tamo ikalamiyaęž‰, baęž‰bene baęž‰ma tetelo ibaęž‰te haęž‰gahaęž‰ koe ipuwalo ko temeteme biyaęž‰tawahana. Baęž‰moe baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ puyaęž‰te baęž‰ma tetelo kuba ododili ipuwalo demedehona, wadiyala ibaęž‰te baęž‰bi tawakalubino temeteme komo ba emalagidolo hidohido ukui nuwataęž‰menaęž‰ ibaęž‰te atu kuba huiya lawekapomaęž‰.   
\p
\v 8 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ puyaęž‰te diya gabodo laęž‰ ipuwamo daęž‰paęž‰paęž‰laęž‰hui, baęž‰bi dubate baęž‰ atumu ibino kateneno kuba ododili ubi gabodo ibino ape baęž‰bo kubahilamenaka. Baęž‰gala ibaęž‰te Godotamo papamilaęž‰hale ubihaęž‰maęž‰ edaęž‰halo Hunu Haboeno nopopi baęž‰bo iduduputilamenaka, mabu baęž‰bako awagaha ukui komate ibaęž‰tamo hiyolo ikulinaka.  
\v 9 Huiyatiya wadiyala laęž‰le Hunu Haboeno nopopino Gawadubu Maikolokono komo nemalagidolalaęž‰, ebeno helo konomola huiyatiya ebete baęž‰be komomaęž‰ kawagahanahaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ keba tetelo ebete Mosesekono hoe ape lawemaęž‰ Saitanakobaęž‰ dolowabeletihuiyaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ebete Saitanatamo eta iduduputimi tabo goeheno naęž‰goiyaęž‰, â€śKodawa Godote haęž‰kiya ebeno tabamo amaęž‰ koduhimimaęž‰naęž‰ta, huiyatiya naeno heloamo nale amaęž‰tamo eta komo aęž‰kododaęž‰mo!â€ť  
\v 10 Huiyatiya laęž‰ ipuwalo daęž‰polaęž‰na baęž‰bi dubuino komo eba kaęž‰nahaęž‰. Ibaęž‰te Hunu Haboeno komokomo iyaęž‰tawahaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ibaęž‰te baęž‰be haboeno nopopino komomaęž‰ ibi iduduputilame tabo begaęž‰lana. Aęž‰iye! Ibaęž‰te kapiya komo iyaęž‰tawahanomola, baęž‰be komo baęž‰ baęž‰moe hopoeno katenaęž‰mo wapataęž‰lame gabola, iyo, ibi baęž‰ tumu goegoe keba kaęž‰nalaęž‰kaęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰nala mabu ibaęž‰te hidohido ukuihino dito emedehona! Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, ibino kateneno ubi komate ibi hibilo kanakapulamemaęž‰naęž‰.   
\p
\v 11 Iyo, Godote ibino kuba huiya ibaęž‰tamo dikalamemene baęž‰be kuba huiya konomomaęž‰ kedaęž‰maęž‰ne, mabu ibaęž‰te Kaęž‰inikono gabodo tolame yaęž‰lo aęž‰tupuimiyaęž‰. Baęž‰gala ibi Baęž‰ilamako keba kaęž‰nalaęž‰kaęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰nala, ibaęž‰te mani koamo emalagidololo koko kuba komokomo baęž‰bo ododilinaka. Baęž‰gala ibi Kolako huiyamaęž‰ edaęž‰hana, baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ibaęž‰te Godotamo papamilaęž‰ha ubihinola, baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibila, Godote Kolakono kuba mabumaęž‰ ebe keba kaęž‰na kanakapumiyaęž‰, ebete ibi baęž‰ atumu kohawaminadigalemaęž‰ne.\f * \fr 1.11 \ft Buka kaęž‰lamiholedawa, amaęž‰ Kaęž‰inikono komo iyaęž‰tawamaęž‰ dewagelemenaęž‰, wadiyala amaęž‰ Tupuilamehole Mabu Buka 4.1-16 numiyaęž‰. Baęž‰gala amaęž‰ Baęž‰ilamakono komo iyaęž‰tawamaęž‰ dewagelemenaęž‰, wadiyala amaęž‰ Nabas Kaęž‰lamihole 22.1â€“25.9 naęž‰kumiyaęž‰. Baęž‰gala amaęž‰ Kolakono komo iyaęž‰tawamaęž‰ dewagelemenaęž‰, wadiyala amaęž‰ Nabas Kaęž‰lamihole 16.1-50 naęž‰kumiyaęž‰.\f*   
\p
\v 12 Numaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipino kapiyuimi poko baaęž‰ naha tetelo, baęž‰bi dubuino komo baęž‰ hido baaęž‰ ipuwalo daęž‰polaęž‰na baęž‰bi kuba nene huiyala, mabu baaęž‰ naha ipuwalo hilopohenola, iyo, ibi haęž‰kiya ibi kapiya bemalagidolena. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hopote gagalemaęž‰ dedaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo huhuti daęž‰wadahenako baęž‰bi bubuti dito kopokoaęž‰tahalemaęž‰naęž‰ huiyatiya wegolate aęž‰koamene, baęž‰bi dubu baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰nala mabu ibaęž‰te tawakalubaęž‰tamo giba aęž‰kikalamaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰gala baęž‰bi dubu baęž‰ nolohohaęž‰ gao kehala, mabu ko gogote daęž‰pemene ibino haha daęž‰pemagobelelamemene hakamo dito kopiyaęž‰hekemaęž‰ne, iyo, ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰te baęž‰ba kaęž‰na wibonomo kowibohomaęž‰naęž‰.  
\v 13 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ komo netewa go tabote baęž‰bi dubuino komo hawakalimimaęž‰ baęž‰polaęž‰na. Dopo go taboeno komo baęž‰ma kaęž‰nala, baęž‰bi dubuino hilopo ododili komo baęž‰ koko gawiyate hununomamo daęž‰pakaminanaka baęž‰ba kaęž‰nala, baęž‰gala eta go tabo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na itana, baęž‰bi dubu baęž‰ du ipuwalo kekaęž‰kekaęž‰lo daęž‰wapataęž‰lamena baęž‰bi oloki huiyala. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Godote ibi mabumaęž‰ kebe du bobo konomo yaęž‰lo dododilamiyaęž‰, ebete ibi baęž‰bamo konoelamemaęž‰ne ibaęž‰te emedena tetelo baęž‰bolo temetemaęž‰go konemedehonamaęž‰.   
\p
\v 14 Numaęž‰laęž‰, Aęž‰daęž‰mekono eyoni gugudi hiliyonomo ipuwalo Inokote baęž‰ saęž‰baęž‰ni badininipaloeno dopo dubu gudumaęž‰ ediyaęž‰, baęž‰gala ebe baęž‰ Godokono ukui hawakalimidawa etala. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ baęž‰moe Inokote baęž‰bi kuba dubuino komomaęž‰ yaęž‰lo tetelo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na goiyaęž‰, â€śNumaęž‰laęž‰, Kodawa Godote ebeno mumulunomo talona nopopaęž‰go pete,  
\v 15 ebete hopo habanapino komokomo hiliyonomo ba panagilamelelame ebeno ubi komamo papamilaęž‰hahaęž‰ tawakalubaęž‰tamo kuba huiya kopikalamemaęž‰ne. Iyo, ibaęž‰te Godotamo kebe kuba komokomo dododilinaka baęž‰gala ebetamo kebe kuba tabo daęž‰gaęž‰lanaka, baęž‰bi komokomomaęž‰ kuba huiyate ibaęž‰tamo hibilo kopemaęž‰ne.â€ť  
\v 16 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰moi kuba ododilipino komo hidamo niyaęž‰tawahalaęž‰. Ibaęž‰godolo ubihaęž‰ tabo gaęž‰la konomola, baęž‰gala ibi haęž‰kiya ibino kuba ulameheno komopi kubapimaęž‰ kaęž‰laminaka. Ibaęž‰te ibino kateneno ubi gabodo wapataęž‰lamemaęž‰ helohelonomola, baęž‰gala ibi haęž‰kiya ibi awagaminalelo eta lumagi haęž‰da amiho gabodo daęž‰milimihomenaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ibaęž‰te ubi bihatena ibino tabo olamagi komodo ebegodone eta hido komo dito kolawemaęž‰.   
\s1 Yudate Hibimaęž‰ Midipi Heluilamemaęž‰ Tabo Komokomo Dolamagiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 17 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono oelamepi dubate laęž‰ dopamo daęž‰kiyalamiyaęž‰la, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰be tabo gala hidamo naęž‰kemalagidolalaęž‰.  
\v 18 Ibaęž‰te laęž‰tamo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na gaęž‰luyaęž‰, â€śKuititi tetelo kubapaęž‰te Godokono ubi komamo papamilaęž‰ha ubihaęž‰maęž‰ edaęž‰halo ibino kateneno ubi gabodo ba wapataęž‰lame laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi kiyaęž‰daęž‰latelemaęž‰naęž‰ta.â€ť  
\v 19 Numaęž‰laęž‰, Yaęž‰sukunu oelamepino tabo baęž‰ hibila. Baęž‰moi kuba ododilipi baęž‰ laęž‰eno kapiyuimi ipuwalo anagiyaęž‰mida komo dododina baęž‰moi baęž‰bi tawakalubila, iyo, ibaęž‰te ibino kateneno ubi komamo ba papamilaęž‰hale, Godokono Gobogobote ibi ipuwalo kemedenahaęž‰.   
\p
\v 20 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komo talonanomomaęž‰ gaęž‰late kodakodalo ba lawe baęž‰bo napepehonalaęž‰, baęž‰gala laęž‰ Godokono Gobogoboeno heloamo ebetamo naęž‰toetoehonalaęž‰.  
\v 21 Baęž‰bene laęž‰le Godokono malemale emalagidolo ipuwalo demedehonama, baęž‰be komo miyaęž‰paheno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono pe komo naęž‰latiminalaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, ebete daęž‰pemene laęž‰le kebe kuba komokomo dododilinakuima, ebete baęž‰bi kuba hiliyonomo egebolelame tabo polamagiti wibohaęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰ laęž‰tamo baęž‰bo kopikalamemaęž‰naęž‰ta.   
\p
\v 22 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo puyaęž‰te kodakodalo laęž‰motaęž‰hanaheno ukui gagagagamaęž‰ dedaęž‰hanaka, laęž‰ ibi malemalelo ba emalagidole ibi nowalubilinakuyaęž‰laęž‰,  
\v 23 iyo, baęž‰moe modobo tete ba itana, wadiyala laęž‰ ibi Saitanakono koe ipuwane tiyonomolo nuluhukulatelaęž‰laęž‰, ibaęž‰te ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo Yaęž‰sugodone kolawemaęž‰. Baęž‰gala wadiyala laęž‰ komo kuba ododilipi atumu malemalelo ba emalagidole naęž‰kowalubilaęž‰laęž‰. Huiyatiya laęž‰ hidamo, ibi ba owalubili ibino kuba ododili komokomo kokohaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰kagaęž‰lamata! Numaęž‰laęž‰, ibaęž‰te ibino kateneno kuba ubilo dododilinaka, baęž‰bi komo baęž‰ ibino pupulino ilina huiyala, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰bi dalowaęž‰go kaliko ubihaęž‰maęž‰ edaęž‰halo laęž‰eno kokotamo akologiholaęž‰laęž‰, ibino kuba dalowaęž‰ komote laęž‰tamo pekapomaęž‰.   
\s1 Yudate Leta Kuititi Hapulu Godoko Milimiho Tabo Dolamagiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 24 O hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰laęž‰, aeno Hido Helodawate bemedena, ebe modobola laęž‰ ba aęž‰gaęž‰lulatele laęž‰le aęž‰kagudaęž‰mata. Baęž‰ hibila, ebete laęž‰ kubahaęž‰pimaęž‰ midiliti, baęž‰bene ko kalakalanomago ebete laęž‰ ebeno aęž‰laęž‰mina holoholo hapuamo komagahelemaęž‰naęž‰ta.  
\v 25 Ebe kapiya baęž‰ Godotela, ebete aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ipuwado aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawamaęž‰ edaęž‰na. Baęž‰ hibila, ebeno awagaha komo baęž‰gala ebeno hido aęž‰laęž‰mina komo, ebeno konomo helo baęž‰gala ebeno ko gawadubu komo, baęž‰moi komate dopamo tupuimi mabuni ebegodolo polaęž‰namaęž‰! Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala baęž‰ma tetelo baęž‰gala emedena emedena tetelo baęž‰moi atu komate ebe kapiyagodolo naęž‰kapolaęž‰namenaęž‰!  
\p Baęž‰moe baęž‰ naeno tabo kuititila. Baęž‰baęž‰la.   